{"tid":920623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【對抗監控】Google員工告密 阻開發審查版搜尋器進軍中國","createTime":"2018-11-29T03:05:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T08:36:44.000Z","uid":147376,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2b0925203395a8340a5b6ac70cc076c458802ddf","tid":920623,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T03:05:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181128/58967000\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181128%2F58967000&d=U0Pt4ZSIax%2BM6%2FJa6Mfzr6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=15af6349\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181128%2F58967000&h=072fb7fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181128/58967000</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網絡巨擘Google一群員工，周二早上發表聯署公開信，要求公司停止開發符合中國審查要求的搜尋引擎「蜻蜓計劃」（Project Dragonfly），並要公司承諾對這項計劃的告密者作出保障。<br />\n<br />\n聯署者共12人，包括多名軟件工程師，以及Google開放研究團隊（Google Open Research）首席成員Meredith Whittaker。信中表指，「蜻蜓計畫」是Google為了符合中國監控而努力開發的搜尋引擎項目；數月來，成千上萬的員工發聲，強調這類審查有人權疑慮，國際人權組織和調查記者也都得到警告，但公司領導層回應無法令人滿意。他們已和國際特赦組織合作，呼籲Google取消計劃。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle行政總裁皮查（Sundar Pichai）上月承認，正在研究能在中國運作的審查版搜尋引擎。由於中國審查機制嚴格，外國搜尋引擎幾乎都撤出中國巿場，皮查表示，中國巿場是獨特挑戰，想知道如果谷歌在中國營運，會是什麼樣子。<br />\n<br />\n信中強調，反對「能讓強權壓迫弱勢者的審查技術」，而不是反對中國。中國政府不是唯一打壓言論自由、監控並鎮壓異己的人。但中國政府擴大監控，使用網路科技大規模監控人民，以此作為社會信用評價，侵害維吾爾人和人權份子；若「蜻蜓計劃」在此時開供應技術的先例，難保集團未來不會對其他國家作出類似讓步。<br />\n<br />\n除了監控，「蜻蜓計劃」還會幫助政府散播有利的假新聞，打壓其他意見。聯署者表示，加入Google就業，原是贊同公司的價值觀，但現在已不再相信公司。「Google太強大，但不負責任，我們應該知道我們正在創造什麼，並在這些重要決策中擁有話語權。」"},{"pid":"df7864b54f59a4e1fe4a38d26f5bea601c4c068a","tid":920623,"uid":18569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T03:08:30.000Z","msg":"為左賺支那條水喉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到兩邊唔喺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7910894e636f779c02cea47bc0d123b0e7950db","tid":920623,"uid":60057,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T04:33:19.000Z","msg":"Don't be evil?<br />\n現實係: Don't be angel!"},{"pid":"33a661ebda935b26b2a42fd7e5ec85fff3f3a9a8","tid":920623,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T04:36:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ec5f180143d832d23c1adae28431898108a15e0","tid":920623,"uid":60287,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T04:38:23.000Z","msg":"支耶，印度，猶太<br />\n三大仆街人種"},{"pid":"be80c26da317ce929d3cd83a49febf9587c19e1e","tid":920623,"uid":22554,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"c7910894e636f779c02cea47bc0d123b0e7950db","tid":920623,"uid":60057,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T04:33:19.000Z","msg":"Don't be evil?<br />\n現實係: Don't be angel!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T04:40:12.000Z","msg":"無計, 上左市就要受股東壓力<br />\n只有私人公司先可以鍾意點就點"},{"pid":"6e562a53d9ec9c50a41c5cb66be2e9fa879934df","tid":920623,"uid":190876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ec5f180143d832d23c1adae28431898108a15e0","tid":920623,"uid":60287,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T04:38:23.000Z","msg":"支耶，印度，猶太<br />\n三大仆街人種"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T04:50:40.000Z","msg":"蝻亞同埋黑鬼咪仲垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85ccb20ee54e91ec80007b1a094b91f684400abe","tid":920623,"uid":60287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e562a53d9ec9c50a41c5cb66be2e9fa879934df","tid":920623,"uid":190876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ec5f180143d832d23c1adae28431898108a15e0","tid":920623,"uid":60287,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T04:38:23.000Z","msg":"支耶，印度，猶太<br />\n三大仆街人種"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T04:50:40.000Z","msg":"蝻亞同埋黑鬼咪仲垃圾<img src=\"/a